attributionInfo.brokerName: Douglas Elliman Real Estate - Park Plaza

description: Beautiful 1 bed in the coveted FP3 building on Congress Street in the heart of the Seaport District’s vibrant Fort Point neighborhood. This 790 sq.ft. residence is efficiently laid out with a formal entry foyer, distinct bedroom area with closet and a generously sized living area. The sleek kitchen, designed by Arclinea, features Silestone countertops & stainless-steel appliances including a Bosch dishwasher & Fisher-Paykel refrigerator. Additional unit features include central air, in-unit laundry, high ceilings, built-out closets & recessed lighting with recent updates of fresh paint, refinished floors and chic lighting upgrades. Building amenities include 24/7 concierge, elevator, common roof deck with gas grill, bike storage & a rotating in-house art gallery. This is a tremendous opportunity to live in the center of it all being just steps to Trader Joes, Seaport, South Station transit, Waterfront/Financial District, Logan Airport & many of Boston’s trendiest restaurants and shops.
